name: Voices from Beyond
description:
Halloween series composed of three artworks, "Lady of the Night", "Voices from Beyond" and "Cry of Silence".

Voices from Beyond

"All that could be heard were like voices in the night,
the whispers that echoed through the darkness,
The eternal reflection of chaos.
The chaos that trembled like candle flames,
The candle that illuminated the unknown. 

A cold smile hovered in the air,
It seemed like death 
But even she didn't want to be there.
The unknown flirted with like voices,
And the night flirted with chaos".
